description:
Natch Beaut host Jackie Johnson joins Kate on this mini-episode! They lend advice to a woman who’s not feeling appreciated by her family, discuss their favorite affordable makeup brushes, and reminisce about past beauty mistakes. Plus, Kate responds to listeners who wrote in about a past mini-episode discussion about an unwanted third pregnancy, and shares exciting news from a listener featured on a previous episode.

To leave a voicemail for a future episode, call 781-591-0390. You can also email the podcast at forever35podcast@gmail.com.

This episode is sponsored by:

  • Stitch Fix - Get started today at stitchfix.com/forever35 and get an extra 25% off when you keep all items in your box.
